  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-04-11",
    "date": "2022-09-16T10:49:59Z",
    "text": "Temperature Endorsement for Multi-Peril Policies or the TEMP Act \n\nThis bill directs the Federal Crop Insurance Corporation to conduct or enter into contracts to carry out research and development regarding a temperature-based index policy to insure crops on a nationally-available basis against losses due to a frost or cold weather event, including research to evaluate the effectiveness of risk management tools with respect to low frequency and catastrophic loss weather events."
